text: The 1960 Atlantic hurricane season began June 1, 1960 and ended November 30, 1960. This season had low activity, with only 7 storms. This season featured the powerful, Hurricane Donna and also Hurricane Ethel. ==Storms== *Tropical Storm One *Hurricane Abby *Tropical Storm Brenda *Hurricane Cleo *Hurricane Donna *Hurricane Ethel *Tropical Storm Florence ==Unused names== * * * * * * * * * * * * * * * ==Retirement== The name "Donna" was retired. ==Other websites== * Monthly Weather Review 1960 Atlantic hurricane season Category:1960s in weather
title: 1960 Atlantic hurricane season
